com.craftfire.commons.util
Class AbstractValueHolder

java.lang.Object
  com.craftfire.commons.util.AbstractValueHolder
All Implemented Interfaces:
ValueHolder
Direct Known Subclasses:
DataField, ValueHolderBase, YamlNode
public abstract class AbstractValueHolder
extends Object
implements ValueHolder

An abstract implementation of ValueHolder.

It redirects all getters without default value to ones with default value, using null, 0 or false as the default value.
